_sText: This map has taken me quite some time to make. And thankyou to PlastiC_HEad for compiling this map becuase my poor pc couldnt handle it. I looked at an overview of Frostfire and 1 by 1 made this map. Please note it is only a beta and all betas have tiny little errors. The screenshots may look a little dark but its better in-game!!! Hope you like it. I'll soon include a .NAV EDIT: I made the entire map a little brighter!
